<h2>Rules for the Game</h2>

<p>Select a coloumn and your piece will go to the lowest row in that column.  Try to get four of your pieces to line up, either horizontally, vertically, or diagonally.</p>
<p>Before each turn answer a math question.  If you answer after 2 minutes have passed or if you answer incorrectly, you lose your turn.</p>
<p>Each time you get four of your pieces to line up, either horizontally, vertically, or diagonally you make a score</p>
<p>When the board is full, the player with the highest score wins</p>
<p>You cannot start a new game unless you cancel the game or finish the current game</p>
